name: Negative Creep
wikiSummary: Featuring two grubby riffs and a whole heap of Cobain's self-pitying, self-loathing, it's Bleach's most dead-eyed wail and Cobain's first attempt at self-analysis.  "I just thought of myself as a negative person," he explained.
wikiText:
Featuring two grubby riffs and a whole heap of Cobain's self-pitying, self-loathing, it's Bleach's most dead-eyed wail and Cobain's first attempt at self-analysis.
 
 "I just thought of myself as a negative person," he explained.
